== 研究方法 ==
对语言的研究可以分为共时和历时两种：
* 共时是指对某一历史时期的语言进行研究，例如对[[现代汉语|现代汉语]]的研究。
* 历时是指对语言从一个时代到另一个时代的历史进行研究。
===理论語言學===
[[理论语言学|理论语言学]]用于考察人类语言的共同规律和普遍特征。从具体语言中找出普遍的系统的理论和规律。

==语言理论==
[[File:Ferdinand_de_Saussure.jpg|thumb]]提出一般语言学将语言研究为意义和形式的平衡系统。]]
===人文语言学===
人文语言学的基本原则是语言是人创造的发明。语言研究的[[符号学|符号学]]传统认为语言是一种[[符号系统|符号系统]]，它产生于意义和形式的相互作用。<ref>{{cite book|last=Nöth|first=Winfried|title=Handbook of Semiotics|publisher=Indiana University Press|date=1990|url=https://salahlibrary.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/handbook-of-semiotics.pdf|isbn=978-0-253-20959-7|access-date=2021-08-04|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308052018/https://salahlibrary.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/handbook-of-semiotics.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>语言结构的组织被认为是计算性的。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hjelmslev|first=Louis|title=Prolegomena to a Theory of Language|publisher=University of Wisconsin Press|date=1969|orig-year=First published 1943|isbn=0-299-02470-9|author-link=Louis_Hjelmslev}}</ref>语言学本质上被认为与社会和文化科学有关，因为不同的语言是由社会互动中的社区塑造的。<ref>{{cite book|last=de Saussure|first=Ferdinand|title=Course in general linguistics|place=New York|publisher=Philosophy Library|date=1959|orig-year=First published 1916|url=https://monoskop.org/images/0/0b/Saussure_Ferdinand_de_Course_in_General_Linguistics_1959.pdf|isbn=978-0-231-15727-8|author-link=Ferdinand_de_Saussure|access-date=2021-08-04|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414113626/https://monoskop.org/images/0/0b/Saussure_Ferdinand_de_Course_in_General_Linguistics_1959.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>代表语言人文观的语言学流派包括结构语言学等。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Theory of language: a taxonomy|url=https://link.springer.com/10.1007/s43545-021-00085-x|last=Austin|first=Patrik|date=2021-03|journal=SN Social Sciences|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s43545-021-00085-x|volume=1|pages=78|language=en|issn=2662-9283}}</ref>

结构分析意味着解剖每一层：语音、形态、句法和话语，到最小的单位。这些被收集到清单中（例如音素、语素、词汇类、短语类型），以研究它们在结构和层的层次结构中的相互联系。<ref>{{cite book|last=Schäfer|first=Roland|title=Einführung in die grammatische Beschreibung des Deutschen (2nd ed.)|place=Berlin|publisher=Language Science Press|date=2016|url=https://www.oapen.org/download?type=document&docid=620310|isbn=978-1-537504-95-7|access-date=2021-08-04|archive-date=2017-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728232919/http://oapen.org/download?type=document&docid=620310|dead-url=no}}</ref>功能分析为结构分析增加了语义角色和每个单元的其他功能角色的分配。例如，名词短语可以作为句子的语法主语或宾语，或者作为语义代理或患者。<ref>{{cite book|last=Halliday & Matthiessen|title=An Introduction to Functional Grammar (3rd ed.)|place=London|publisher=Hodder|date=2004|url=http://www.uel.br/projetos/ppcat/pages/arquivos/RESOURCES/2004_HALLIDAY_MATTHIESSEN_An_Introduction_to_Functional_Grammar.pdf|isbn=0-340-76167-9|author-link=M. A. K. Halliday|access-date=2021-08-04|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303145809/http://www.uel.br/projetos/ppcat/pages/arquivos/RESOURCES/2004_HALLIDAY_MATTHIESSEN_An_Introduction_to_Functional_Grammar.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

功能语言学或功能语法是结构语言学的一个分支。在人文背景下，[[结构主义|结构主义]]和[[机能主义心理学派|功能主义]]这两个术语与它们在其他人文科学中的含义有关。形式结构主义和功能结构主义之间的区别在于它们对为什么语言具有它们所具有的属性这一问题的回答。功能解释意味着语言是交流的工具，或者交流是语言的主要功能。因此，语言形式是根据它们的功能价值或用途来解释的。其他结构主义方法认为形式遵循双边和多层语言系统的内部机制。<ref>{{cite book|last=Daneš|first=František|editor=Dirven & Fried|title=Functionalism in Linguistics|publisher=John Benjamins|date=1987|pages=3–38|chapter=On Prague school functionalism in linguistics|isbn=978-90-272-1524-6}}</ref>

===生物语言学===
[[认知语言学|认知语言学]]和[[生成语法|生成语法]]等方法研究语言认知，以期揭示语言的[[生物学|生物学]]基础。在生成语法中，这些基础被认为来自先天的语法知识。因此，该方法的核心关注点之一是发现语言知识的哪些方面是遗传的。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Structures, Not Strings: Linguistics as Part of the Cognitive Sciences|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26564247|last=Everaert|first=Martin B. H.|last2=Huybregts|first2=Marinus A. C.|date=2015-12|journal=Trends in Cognitive Sciences|issue=12|doi=10.1016/j.tics.2015.09.008|volume=19|pages=729–743|issn=1879-307X|pmid=26564247|last3=Chomsky|first3=Noam|last4=Berwick|first4=Robert C.|last5=Bolhuis|first5=Johan J.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Chomsky|first=Noam|title=The Minimalist Program (2nd ed.)|publisher=MIT Press|date=2015|isbn=978-0-262-52734-7|authorlink=诺姆·乔姆斯基}}</ref>

相反，认知语言学拒绝先天语法的概念，并研究人类思维如何从事件图式中创建语言结构<ref name="Arbib_2015">{{cite book|last=Arbib|first=Michael A.|editor=MacWhinney & O'Grady|title=Handbook of Language Emergence|publisher=Wiley|date=2015|pages=81–109|chapter=Language evolution – an emergentist perspective|isbn=978-1-118-34613-6}}</ref>以及认知约束和偏见对人类语言的影响。<ref>{{cite book|last=Tobin|first=Vera|editor=Borkent|title=Language and the Creative Mind|publisher=Chicago University Press|date=2014|pages=347–363|chapter=Where do cognitive biases fit into cognitive linguistics?|chapter-url=http://www.academia.edu/download/37200544/WhereDoCognitiveBiases.pdf|isbn=978-90-272-8643-7}}</ref>与[[神經語言規劃|神经语言编程]]类似，语言是通过感官来接触的。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Metaphors and Neuro-linguistic Programming*|url=https://cgscholar.com/bookstore/works/metaphors-and-neurolinguistic-programming|last=Guarddon Anelo|first=María del Carmen|date=2010|journal=The International Journal of Interdisciplinary Social Sciences: Annual Review|issue=7|doi=10.18848/1833-1882/CGP/v05i07/51812|volume=5|pages=151–162|issn=1833-1882}}</ref><ref name="Ibarretxe-Antuñano_2002">{{cite journal|title=MIND-AS-BODY as a Cross-linguistic Conceptual Metaphor|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/272507067|last=Ibarretxe-Antuñano|first=Iraide|date=2002|journal=Miscelánea|issue=1|volume=25|pages=93–119|access-date=2020-07-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The cognitive psychological reality of image schemas and their transformations|url=https://www.degruyter.com/document/doi/10.1515/cogl.1995.6.4.347/html|last=Gibbs|first=Raymond W.|last2=Colston|first2=Herbert L.|date=1995-01|journal=Cognitive Linguistics|issue=4|doi=10.1515/cogl.1995.6.4.347|volume=6|pages=347–378|language=en|issn=0936-5907}}</ref>认知语言学家通过寻找与感觉运动图式相关的表达来研究知识的体现。<ref name="Luodonpää-Manni&Viimaranta_2017">{{cite book|last=Luodonpää-Manni, Penttilä & Viimaranta|url=https://www.cambridgescholars.com/product/978-1-4438-7325-3|title=Empirical Approaches to Cognitive Linguistics: Analyzing Real-Life Data|date=2017|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-4438-7325-3|editor=Luodonpää-Manni & Viimaranta|chapter=Introduction|access-date=2020-06-30|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430030002/https://www.cambridgescholars.com/product/978-1-4438-7325-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一种密切相关的方法是进化语言学,<ref>{{cite journal|title=Integrating cognitive linguistics and language evolution research|url=https://apcz.umk.pl/czasopisma/index.php/THS/article/viewFile/ths-2014-002/4967|last=Pleyer & Winters|journal=Theoria et Historia Scientiarum|doi=10.12775/ths-2014-002|year=2014|volume=11|pages=19–44|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309004449/https://apcz.umk.pl/czasopisma/index.php/THS/article/viewFile/ths-2014-002/4967|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中包括将语言单位作为文化复制器的研究。<ref>{{cite book|last=Evans & Green|title=Cognitive Linguistics. An Introduction|publisher=Routledge|date=2006|isbn=0-7486-1831-7}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Integrating Cognitive Linguistics and language evolution research|url=http://apcz.pl/czasopisma/index.php/THS/article/view/ths-2014-002|last=Pleyer|first=Michael|last2=Winters|first2=James|date=2015-01-30|journal=Theoria et Historia Scientiarum|doi=10.12775/ths-2014-002|volume=11|pages=19|issn=0867-4159}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite journal|title=Evolutionary Linguistics|url=https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.anthro.37.081407.085156|last=Croft|first=William|date=2008-10-01|journal=Annual Review of Anthropology|issue=1|doi=10.1146/annurev.anthro.37.081407.085156|volume=37|pages=219–234|language=en|issn=0084-6570}}</ref>可以研究语言如何复制和适应个人或语言社区的思想。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Complex adaptive systems and the origins of adaptive structure: what experiments can tell us|url=https://www.research.ed.ac.uk/portal/files/8777212/complex_adaptive_systems.pdf|last=Cornish, Tamariz & Kirby|journal=Language Learning|doi=10.1111/j.1467-9922.2009.00540.x|year=2009|volume=59|pages=187–205|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112190847/https://www.research.ed.ac.uk/portal/files/8777212/complex_adaptive_systems.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Language Structures May Adapt to the Sociolinguistic Environment, but It Matters What and How You Count: A Typological Study of Verbal and Nominal Complexity|last=Sinnemäki & Di Garbo|journal=Frontiers in Psychology|doi=10.3389/fpsyg.2018.01141|year=2018|volume=9|pages=187–205|pmc=6102949|pmid=30154738}}</ref>构造语法是将[[模因|模因]]概念应用于句法研究的框架。<ref name="Dahl_2001">{{cite journal|title=Grammaticalization and the life cycles of constructions|last=Dahl|first=Östen|date=2001|journal=RASK – Internationalt Tidsskrift for Sprog og Kommunikation|volume=14|pages=91–134}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Transitions: The Evolution of Linguistic Replicators|title=The Language Phenomenon|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/978-3-642-36086-2_6|publisher=Springer Berlin Heidelberg|date=2013|location=Berlin, Heidelberg|isbn=978-3-642-36085-5|pages=121–138|doi=10.1007/978-3-642-36086-2_6|first=Simon|last=Kirby|editor-first=P.-M.|editor-last=Binder}}</ref><ref name="Zehentner_2019">{{cite book|last=Zehentner|first=Eva|title=Competition in Language Change: the Rise of the English Dative Alternation|publisher=De Gruyter Mouton|year=2019|isbn=978-3-11-063385-6}}</ref><ref name="MacWhinney_2015">{{cite book|last=MacWhinney|first=Brian|title=Handbook of Language Emergence|date=2015|publisher=Wiley|isbn=978-1-118-34613-6|editor=MacWhinney & O'Grady|pages=1–31|chapter=Introduction – language emergence}}</ref>

